name: Gate Traveler
description:
Hello everyone! Welcome to Gate traveler.

This is game that was made the Let's Create Game Jam #1

This is the first project I have ever made using the Unreal engine 4 and also one of the first time actually using it. I had alot of fun learning the game engine and developing this game.

Keep in mind: I entered the game jam 1 week before submission and at the start of school so I have been really busy. Something that I would have wanted is a better level design. I tried to be as creative as I could using the short time I had.

I hope you like it tho!
